        "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64\nOffice Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT\nTO : Director, FBI DATE: May 5, 1959\n21\nSAC, Seattle (62-1729)\nSUBJECT: AERIAL PHENOMENA RESEARCH GROUP-\nMISCELLANEOUS\nRe Birmingham letter 4-21-59."
